ke":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:14:31.000Z","msg":"要大肆宣傳set 一個deadline.<br />\n講明<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>若果deadline前政府都唔回應五大訴求, 會行動升級</strong></span> 後果自負<br />\n<br />\n用意: 先小人後君子<br />\n1)迫使政府回應<br />\n2)市民有心理準備當日會有行動<br />\n3)令市民知道當天有行動係源於政府唔回應 <br />\n    (令佢地明白若果政府肯回應就唔會有行動阻礙到佢番工, 出街)<br />\n<br />\n<strong>1) 五大訴求</strong><br />\n一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況, 解散、追究及重組警隊<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選<br />\n<br />\n[下一步棋] 救香港 Set Deadline 行動升級 (幫推)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1497453\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1497453</a>"},{"pid":"f94d93639e70f5a9aa8d5ec846240927f419f77d","tid":1497534,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:15:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bd493fd317e6f3fe508002737ed9d8a9d820459","tid":1497534,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:17:37.000Z","msg":"「千字文」毋忘初衷，我「反思」故我在<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1497022\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1497022</a>"},{"pid":"eda461960241789d74a612134e317a82fefdb36f","tid":1497534,"uid":152241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:21:05.000Z","msg":"又洗白"},{"pid":"270b8c5748b7a0fef31e5b3c3aac2f65ceaaccac","tid":1497534,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:25:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f799648bbaf564ccaaf8c0e34ba44359bdbc9a4","tid":1497534,"uid":54415,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:28:41.000Z","msg":"洗你老母呀，一兩個扮講人話就夠呀？兩隻眼，無數斷骨，點計！"},{"pid":"0fff3b4fad8877d7114eebc654ab6548af1fe8c7","tid":1497534,"uid":45320,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:32:11.000Z","msg":"佢fb屌9對示威者呀<br />\n唔好比佢扮野"